title: Shitty First Drafts
content: The author says that almost all good writing begins with bad first drafts. These terrible first efforts, she argues, lead to clarity and sometimes brilliance in our second and third drafts. An encouraging read for anyone discouraged by their initial efforts.

title: Working out to accelerate the benefits of a fast
content: Peter recently whiteboarded out his logic for how he uses his workout on the first day of a fast to accelerate the benefits.
